wm-license-cc-free-to-share-text: dy choipal, dy rheynn, as dy scaalheaney yn obbyr
wm-license-cc-conditions-attribution-tex: Lhisagh oo cur treist chooie, kiarail kiangley da’n chiedoonys, as soilshee ny caghlaaghyn my row lheid jeant. Foddee oo eh y yannoo ayns aght ennagh resoonagh, agh cha nel kied ayd dy haishbyney dy vel y kiedooneyr dy dty phohldall ny yn ymmyd ayd.
wm-license-cc-conditions-share_alike-tex: My vel oo aavestey, caghlaa, ny cur s’odjey rish y stoo, lhisagh oo rheynn dty chohoyrtyssyn fo’n [[ccorg:share-your-work/licensing-considerations/compatible-licenses|chiedoonys cheddin as, ny fo kiedoonys corrym rish]], y chiedoonys bunneydagh.
